  <text_after_fields><para>The VGrp1DIE, VGrp1EIE, VGrp0DIE, and VGrp0EIE fields permit the hypervisor to track the virtual CPU interfaces that are enabled. The hypervisor can then route interrupts that have multiple targets correctly and efficiently, without having to read the virtual CPU interface status.</para>
